-----Original Message-----
From: Palansky, IJay [mailto:IPalansky@wilmer.com]
Sent: Friday, August 24, 2001 4:43 PM
To: Cohen, Louis; 'Jeffrey D. (Dan) Watkiss (E-mail)'; Plotnick, Michael
