 -----Original Message-----
From: 	"Jamie Wimberly" <Benjamin.Wimberly@Verizon.net>@ENRON [mailto:IMCEANOTES-+22Jamie+20Wimberly+22+20+3CBenjamin+2EWimberly+40Verizon+2Enet+3E+40ENRON@ENRON.com] 
