 -----Original Message-----
From: 	"Reilley, Robert R." <breilley@coral-energy.com>@ENRON [mailto:IMCEANOTES-+22Reilley+2C+20Robert+20R+2E+22+20+3Cbreilley+40coral-energy+2Ecom+3E+40ENRON@ENRON.com] 
